```suggestion
{: #ref-to-fig3  title="Deployment Case of NTP in Tidal Networks"}
```

The example should be formatted using JSON.  Please update the example with the following:

```
{
   "ietf-tvr-node:rw node-schedule":{
      "node-id":"192.168.1.101",
      "interface-schedule":{
         "interfaces":[
            {
               "name":"Wlan0",
               "attribute-schedule":{
                  "schedules":[
                     {
                        "schedule-id":"0123456789",
                        "period-start":"2024-10-19T19:00:00",
                        "time-zone-identifier":"Europe/Paris",
                        "duration":43200,
                        "attr-value":{
                           "available":"false"
                        }
                     }
                  ]
               }
            }
         ]
      }
   }
```

}
